# Teams Watcher Prompt Template

When a message arrives in the monitored Teams channel, the agent receives this prompt.

## Placeholders

- `{{SENDER}}` - Display name of the message sender
- `{{CONTENT}}` - The message content
- `{{WEBHOOK}}` - The webhook name for replies (from triggers.json)

## Template

```
[Teams Message from {{SENDER}}]
{{CONTENT}}

---
Respond to this Teams message. Use teams_post_to_configured_channel('{{WEBHOOK}}', your_response) to reply.
```
